narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This was a fantastic course. I learned how to build a solution to a social challenge from the bottom up. We co-created with our communities, and in the end developed a viable solution for improving student mental health. Were actually going forward with our venture (my team) and trying to develop and implement our mobile app product. I cannot do this course justice in a written review. All I can say is that Ive made wonderful friends, found a sense of excitement and purpose, and developed my business savvy, communication skills, and more.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! Teresa is amazing and this course actually shows you how you can practically solve problems. Fantastic class, I had a great team and we are turning our venture from a class project into a real start-up!
